	ir caregivers during the group time. There is also a play time for childre
	n to explore various toys and play activities.\n\nEvent is in English and 
	Mandarin.\n\n-------------------------------------------------------------
	----------------------\n\n萬花筒邊玩邊學®: 孩子與他們的照顧者在小組中一起聽多種語言故事、唱歌並做簡單的手工。萬花筒邊玩
